            <bug_when>2009-09-18 22:46:25 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Documentation for qx.ui.table.Table.setSelectable(bool) indicates that it should change a table&#39;s ability to have selection performed on it. According to Derrell, it currently has no effect. The appropriate behavior (turning off selection in my case) was accomplished by:

table.getSelectionModel().setSelectionMode(qx.ui.table.selection.Model.NO_SELECTION);

which could be made into the underlying method when setSelectable(false) is called. I&#39;m not sure about the appropriate behavior for setSelectable(true); perhaps restoring the default selection mode.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
